🌐 External vs Internal IP
  Every VM gets IPs for communication.

  🌍 External IP (Public IP)
    Accessible from internet
    Used for:
    Web servers
    APIs
    👉 Example:
    User → Internet → External IP → VM
  
  🏠 Internal IP (Private IP)
    Used inside VPC network
    Not accessible from internet
    👉 Example:
    App Server → DB Server (internal IP)
