🚀 Managed Instance Group ---------------
  👉 A service that manages a group of identical VMs automatically using an Instance Template

  ⚙️ Key Features
    🔄 Auto-Healing
    📈 Auto-Scaling
    🌍 Load Balancing Integration
    🔁 Rolling Updates
    📦 Auto-Creation

  🔄 Lifecycle Flow
    Create Instance Template
    Create MIG
    MIG launches VMs
    Attach Load Balancer
    Enable:
    Auto-scaling
    Health checks
